Generic single-database configuration.

## Migration chain

Alembic is the **single migration system** for RegEngine. The `migrations/`
directory of raw SQL files was removed after consolidation (April 2026).

To upgrade to the latest head:

    alembic upgrade head

Run `alembic history` to see the full chain.

## Legacy service migrations

The old service-level Flyway files under `services/*/migrations/V*.sql`
were burned down in #2004. Any active DDL from those files is now
forward-ported through `alembic/versions/`.
